Run locally:

1) Install deps
   npm i

2) Start server
   npm run dev

3) Open in browser
   http://localhost:5173

Endpoints:
- GET /      serves static UI from `public`
- POST /api/echo  {"message":"строка"} -> {"echo":"строка"}
- POST /mcp  JSON-RPC {"jsonrpc":"2.0","method":"tools/echo","params":{"message":"..."},"id":1}

Design reference (Figma): https://www.figma.com/design/Veam9uK0i0yJMtXekQdnQK/by-aleks?node-id=8-40&t=ImzpkJbBXThEFb6G-4